## Overview

FindIt is a full-stack reference application designed to make lost-and-found item reporting simple, reliable, and secure. The platform enables users to register and log in, report lost or found items, search and browse listings, view item details, and contact owners without exposing sensitive owner data.

The project combines a responsive frontend with a Node.js/Express backend, a MySQL database, and a strong quality engineering practice supported by STLC documents, automation suites, and reporting tools.

