## Specifications

### Functional Specifications

- User registration with email, password, and validation.
- User login with JWT-based authentication.
- User dashboard displaying owned lost and found listings.
- Lost item reporting flow with required fields: title, description, category, location, date.
- Found item reporting flow with similar required fields.
- Search and browse functionality with type filters and pagination.
- Item detail pages with contact owner capabilities.
- Update and delete operations restricted to item owners.
- Backend API route security with JWT protection and proper authorization.

### Non-Functional Specifications

- Page load and API response performance targets.
- Responsive UI for desktop and mobile devices.
- Accessibility compliance for keyboard navigation and form labels.
- Security protection via prepared statements, JWT auth, and input validation.
- Maintainability through consistent code standards and modular structure.

